data.description: Come view this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home that sits on 2 acres of usable leveled land. It has original hardwood flooring throughout, heated bathroom floors, formal dining and office at the front entrance. When you step out back you will walk into a 20x17 screened in porch that connects you to your Man Cave or 4th separate bedroom. The beautiful yard is surrounded by mature trees that comes with two storage houses for additional space. So don't wait until it's sold, call today!
